FBIS4-60259 "drnes100_a_94002" FBIS-NES-94-100 Daily Report 23 May 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Senior Officials Dismissed After Prison Breakout Inquiry Senior Officials Dismissed After Prison Breakout Inquiry LD2305203894 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 GMT 23 May 94 LD2305203894 Algiers ENTV Television Network Arabic BFN [Excerpt] An investigation has taken place into a breakout from Tazoult prison on 10 March, the circumstances in which the incident occurred, and the share of responsibility for the incident of public officials. Following the investigation, the governor of Batna Province, the head of security of Batna Province, the head of security of Tazoult district, the director of re-education affairs at the Ministry of Justice, and the Tazoult police chief were dismissed today. The first results of the investigation revealed that the terrorists had benefited from the assistance of two persons working at the police station. [passage omitted]
